h3. Summary
 * Quick Filters on a board are being deselected when navigating away from the board's page. I was able to reproduce this behavior using Chrome, Firefox, and Opera;

h3. Steps to Reproduce
 # Go to any Kanban board and select a quick filter;
 # Click on any other page (e.g. "Releases");
 # Going back to the board no quick filter is selected;
 # _(Note)_ This won't happen if "Project Settings" page is clicked

h3. Expected Results
 * Quick filters would still be selected when navigating away and going back to the board's page (This was true on the previous UI);

h3. Actual Results
 * Filters are being deselected when navigating to another page and going back to the board's page;

h3. Workaround
 * Bookmark URL of the desired board with the quick filter selected;
